# React + Vite Frontend

UI: **shadcn/ui** (Base UI + Tailwind v4). Add components with `npx shadcn@latest add <name>` from `apps/client`. Details → [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md).

- Use `@/components/ui/*` for primitives (Button, Input, Select, Card, Table, Label)
- Functional components + hooks (`useFuelCalculator` for WS lifecycle)
- No fuel formulas in client — server is source of truth
- No submit button; send on every input change
- Show loading/error states; handle reconnect with backoff

```typescript
// ❌ Fuel formulas in client
const fuel = mass * 9.807 * 0.042 - 33
```
